{"id":158356,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/澳广-南澳爆发诺罗病毒疫情/","date":"2011-06-06T08:30:20Z","modified":"2011-06-06T08:30:20Z","title":"澳广 | 南澳爆发诺罗病毒疫情","content":"<div>\n<p>南澳爆发诺罗病毒疫情</p>\n<p>就在欧洲、美洲发生新型大肠杆菌感染疫情之际，澳大利亚南澳州卫生局证实，该州首府阿德雷德有18人感染了诺罗病毒。.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<p>2011 年 06 月 06 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3236343.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3236343.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3236343.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3236343.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3236343.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3236343.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>就在欧洲、美洲发生新型大肠杆菌感染疫情之际，澳大利亚南澳州卫生局证实，该州首府阿德雷德有18人感染了诺罗病毒。</p>\n<p>这种病毒造成严重急性肠胃炎，不过专家预计，所有被感染的病人都能完全康复。</p>\n<p>阿德雷德妇女和儿童医院有9名职员和6名病人被确认染上这种病毒。</p>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" hre